overview:
Oybuzz is pioneering a new model of social advertising that makes advertising easier to find, create, and track in any campaign. The people behind oybuzz include a group of seasoned professionals with over 50 years of collective experience in the IT industry and specifically in the internet & wireless sectors. The team has had extensive international experience in multiple disciplines including sales, corporate and channel marketing, business development, engineering, consulting and professional services. All have held senior level positions in both multi-national corporations as well as start up organizations.

What is all about? The program is free to join; it’s easy to sign-up and requires no technical knowledge. Advertisers offer extensive lines of campaign programs and allows a one stop shop for promoting, marketing and adverting their online business. Oybuzz lets the advertiser search, review, create, edit, launch and track any campaigns here at oybuzz.com. Our concept is simply: Create, Launch, Track!
